  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "🌟 Brand Experience Curator🌟",
  "description": "<h3>🌟 Events Promoter – Be the Voice, Vibe & Vision of Our Events! 🌟</h3><p>Join our <strong>Events Marketing Team </strong>and become the heartbeat behind exciting campaigns and on-ground brand experiences. In this role, you’ll turn ideas into energy, audiences into fans, and events into moments people remember.</p><p>If you’re creative, outgoing, and love bringing brands to life through real connections — this is where you’ll shine.</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>🎯 Drive event awareness through social media, outreach, and creative marketing ideas</p><p>🎤 Represent brands on-site with confidence, energy, and personality</p><p>🎪 Plan and execute promotional activities that attract crowds and boost engagement</p><p>📸 Build hype through content creation, promotions, and face-to-face interactions</p><p>📊 Observe audience responses and share insights to improve future events</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>🎓 Full training provided — no experience needed</p><p>🌱 Positive, supportive environment focused on growth and development</p><p>🚀 Opportunities to build real marketing, communication, and branding skills</p><p>🎉 Team nights & bonding activities — KTV, HDL, KBBQ, Laser Tag & more (let’s gooo!)</p><p><br /><strong>Who You Are</strong></p><p>✨ Energetic, confident, and comfortable engaging with people</p><p>🎨 Creative thinker who enjoys trying new ideas</p><p>🗣 Strong communicator (online and in person)</p><p>🤝 Team player with a positive mindset and willingness to learn</p><p><br /><strong>🌟 Join us and turn every event into a story worth sharing — where your creativity brings brands to life and your energy makes the difference.</strong></p>",
